text.tspan: Mister Pickles is, without a doubt, the world's most
successful businessman. He sells yarn to the cats of
the world and makes so much money that he can buy
at least one extra cat tree. Unfortunately, he is too
large to fit in a cat tree, so he does not buy at least
one extra cat tree. In his spare time he likes to play
with yarn, but denies that he does so: "I would never
dabble in my own product; I could get addicted!" He
has a younger sister (she's coming up soon) whom he
cares for deeply and spoils to hell and back. She's
